  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Go Go Ackman 3 is an Action game, developed by Aspect and published by Banpresto, which was released in Japan in 1995. It is the third and final Go Go Ackman game for the Super Famicom.\n\nThis is the first game in which the series Nemesis, Tenshi, is playable. But due to the fact that Tenshi is an angel he will not collect the souls of the enemies.\n\nGo Go Ackman was created by famous mangaka Akira Toriyama, known for his work on Dragon Ball as well as games such as Chrono Trigger and Dragon Quest.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Due to a change in command in heaven. Tenshi find himself wanted by the Angel Police. The former nemesis joins forces with Ackman to clear his name and figure out who is really pulling the strings. Was he framed or guilty like Ackman? Does Ackman even care?",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    }
  ]
